org.dockbox.selene.api.annotations.event.filter

Annotation Type Filter


  • @Repeatable(value=Filters.class)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Filter
    Indicates whether or not to call an event based on a given filter. A filter includes the parameter to perform a filter on, the FilterTypes to use, and the value it should match. Only applies if a event is an instance of Filterable. Any event implementing Filterable can provide a list of supported params and FilterTypes. It is up to the event to indicate the exact filter implementation based on the information provided.
